track_notes: You must park at the Col de la Sine, plenty room, you will found here some tables if you want have a dinner! Then you walk 20mn until you see the Chapelle St Pons, follow the path until the col Baisse du Brec, at this point you must walk to the right in the middle of a forest, there is no path, but it is easy, on summit there is lot of room for antennas, the landscape is fine.
easy walk for this summit, plenty room on summit for antenna
This is a long walk to this summit, but on your way back you can activate FAM-375. Park at the typical village Bairols. the 2 summits are ok for antenna setup.
